column3: str
Squawk! Trespassing on Ehcatl territory, featherless one is! What business have you with us!?
Squawk! Trespassing on Ehcatl territory, featherless one is! What business have you with us!?
What will you ask?
Tell me about yourself.
What kind of place is this?
Nothing.
Guard territory of Ehcatl, Razel does! Step out of line and gut you with talons, Razel will! Squawk!
Gathering of artisans and engineers, this is. Call ourselves “Ehcatl Nine”!
Drawn by dream of Chief Totoloc, we were... Hmmm. To fly again. Yes. To soar!
Snigger at our dreams, do you? Hmmm? Have last cackle, we will! Caw!
Shipyard of Ehcatl Nine, this is!
Obvious, now, what we do here, yes? Building special airship, we are!
Latest technology! Revolutionary ideas! Bind them together to create unique hybrid vessel, we will!
Privileged to be here, featherless one is! Be sneaky and stealthy, we must! Keep camp secret even from our own kin, we do!
Like that we borrow no-feathers technology, they would not!
Caw! Like that we borrow no-feathers technology, no-feathers would not either!
Hide from both, we do! Secret and safe! Blather about what you see here, featherless one must not!
Betray our trust, and mount featherless one's head on airship prow, Razel will! Squawk!
Squawk! <Split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)/>! Have questions for Razel, do you? Hmmm?
What will you ask?
How fares the Ehcatl Nine?
What do you do here again?
Nothing.
Squawk! Well! Very well, we fare!
Great success, first flight of <Emphasis>Dezul Qualan</Emphasis> was! Very high, it flew! Soared like bird! But satisfied, we are not...
Not until we land upon shores of Ayatlan! Dream yet of that day, we do!
And so work, we shall. Today. Tomorrow. Work until we can climb high above clouds, we will! Squawk!
Squawk! Well! Very well, we fare!
Great success, first flight of <Emphasis>Dezul Qualan</Emphasis> was! Very high, it flew! Soared like bird! But satisfied, we are not...
Not until we land upon shores of Ayatlan! Dream yet of that day, we do!
Hmmm? Making solemn face, featherless one is. Strikes awe into heart, name of Ayatlan does? Yes? Then take you there, perhaps we will!
But now work, we must. Today. Tomorrow. Work until we can climb high above clouds, we will! Squawk!
Fall from airship and bump head, did you? Ehcatl, this is! Shipyard of Ehcatl Nine!
Still seek to improve airship, we do!
Ixal technology, no-feathers technology─it matters not. Only dream of flying.
Kept Ehcatl secret, you have? Yes? Feel sad about gutting <Split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)/>, Razel would.
